stream
BT
/F1 10 Tf
14 TL
54 738 Td
() Tj
T*
(docker compose restart redis) Tj
T*
(- What it is for: Intentionally restart dependency.) Tj
T*
(- Why use it: Failure injection for resilience testing.) Tj
T*
(- Example:) Tj
T*
(    docker compose restart redis) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(docker compose exec redis redis-cli) Tj
T*
(- What it is for: Open Redis CLI inside running container.) Tj
T*
(- Why use it: Validate Redis directly \(PING, GET, INCR\) without network assumptions.) Tj
T*
(- Example:) Tj
T*
(    docker compose exec redis redis-cli) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(docker compose exec <service> sh) Tj
T*
(- What it is for: Open shell inside a service container.) Tj
T*
(- Why use it: Run local checks from container network perspective.) Tj
T*
(- Example:) Tj
T*
(    docker compose exec api sh) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(docker compose exec api wget -qO- http://localhost:3000/readyz) Tj
T*
(- What it is for: Probe API readiness from inside the API container.) Tj
T*
(- Why use it: Matches Compose health check behavior exactly.) Tj
T*
(- Example:) Tj
T*
(    docker compose exec api wget -qO- http://localhost:3000/readyz) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(docker compose up -d --build web) Tj
T*
(- What it is for: Rebuild/restart only web service.) Tj
T*
(- Why use it: Iterate on retry/backoff tuning quickly.) Tj
T*
(- Example:) Tj
T*
(    docker compose up -d --build web) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Supporting Container Command) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(docker run --rm -it --network <project>_default redis:7-alpine redis-cli -h redis) Tj
T*
(- What it is for: Launch temporary Redis CLI container on Compose network.) Tj
T*
(- Why use it: Useful when you do not want to exec into existing Redis container.) Tj
T*
(- Example:) Tj
T*
(    docker run --rm -it --network resilience-08_default redis:7-alpine redis-cli -h redis) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Probe Tools) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(curl) Tj
T*
(- What it is: CLI HTTP client for quick endpoint checks.) Tj
T*
(- What it is for: Verify health/readiness and capture status + body quickly.) Tj
T*
(- Why use it: Available almost everywhere; ideal for repeated probes during failures.) Tj
T*
(- Examples:) Tj
T*
(    curl http://localhost:3000/healthz) Tj
T*
(    curl http://localhost:3000/readyz) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
